      `}</svg></a>{`Third-Party Types`}</h6><p parentName="section">{`If you would like to use types from a third party package, you can just re-export them in your own app. Here's the above example re-visited using some third party typings:`}</p><pre parentName="section"><code parentName="pre" {...{
            "className": "language-ts"
          }}>{`export type * as Spotify from 'spotify-api'
